{"objectClass":"NSDictionary","root":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"62T3W","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"62YPC","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"S67O1","text":"这种把调主音之外的音当作临时主音的方法叫做主音化"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"主音化"},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"3YSX8","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"A86VU","text":"以C大调为例，除了主和弦C之外，F、G、Dm、Am和Em五个和弦分别都能独挑大梁，去做其它调的主和弦，分别是F、G大调以及d、a、e小调。对C大调来说，这些调都是关系比较近的“邻居”，统称副调"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"副调"},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"44805","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"O80G7","text":"主调和声中掺入副调的和弦片段，会产生一种暂时偏离本调的感觉，给和声增添变化，这种技巧中文语境下称为离调"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"离调"},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"5EP85","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"YS755","text":"Y/X:X级和弦的Y级和弦"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"副调和弦记号"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"children2":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"13I5Z","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"85PHO","text":"","isLeft":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"副属和弦","isLeft":true},"1":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"DRT49","text":"副导和弦","isLeft":true},"2":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"PC4TD","text":"副下属和弦","isLeft":true},"3":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"W2EW9","text":"副上主和弦","isLeft":true},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"副调和弦"},"ID":"REP37","style":200,"lineKeepThin":true}